{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779175078053,"sessionID":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_00_GtfA9mZJ7e48Jm34bqeN3984","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md","content":"# DESIGN_SYSTEM_A — Editorial Minimal\n\n**Archetype:** Editorial Minimal\n**Reference Company:** Linear\n**Variant Code:** A\n\n---\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\n**Core Inspiration:**\n- **Linear** — clean, content-first, one action per page, zero visual noise\n- **Stripe** — minimal dashboard, generous whitespace\n- **Apple** — typography as hierarchy, light weight headings\n- **Airbnb** — photography-forward, minimal chrome\n\n**The Three Pillars:**\n- Search & Browsing = Airbnb (photo cards, minimal overlaid text)\n- Admin Dashboard = Linear (content-first, hairline separators)\n- Property Detail = Zillow (structured info, clear hierarchy)\n\n---\n\n## Design System Quick Reference\n\n### Colors\n\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Primary | #4A90D9 | CTA buttons, active links, selected states only |\n| Primary Hover | #3A7BC8 | Button hover |\n| Primary Light | #EBF2FB | Very subtle background tint (rarely used) |\n| Background | #FFFFFF | Pure white page background |\n| Surface | #FFFFFF | Cards (indistinguishable from background) |\n| Surface Elevated | #FAFAFA | Slightly elevated areas |\n| Text Primary | #1A1A1A | Headings, body text |\n| Text Secondary | #6B7280 | Labels, metadata, descriptions |\n| Text Tertiary | #9CA3AF | Placeholders, disabled text |\n| Border | #F3F4F6 | Hairline 0.5px borders |\n| Border Strong | #E5E7EB | Stronger separators |\n| Success | #10B981 | 6px green dot |\n| Warning | #F59E0B | 6px amber dot |\n| Error | #EF4444 | 6px red dot |\n| Sidebar BG | #F8FAFC | Light sidebar background |\n| Sidebar Active | #FFFFFF | Active item highlight |\n\n### Typography\n\n| Level | Size | Weight | Letter Spacing | Usage |\n|-------|------|--------|----------------|-------|\n| H1 | 4.5rem (72px) | 300 | -0.04em | Hero sections only |\n| H2 | 2.25rem (36px) | 300 | -0.02em | Page titles |\n| H3 | 1.5rem (24px) | 400 | -0.01em | Section headings |\n| H4 | 1.125rem (18px) | 500 | normal | Card titles |\n| Body | 1rem (16px) | 400 | normal | Main content |\n| Small | 0.875rem (14px) | 400 | normal | Metadata, labels |\n| Caption | 0.75rem (12px) | 400 | normal | Fine print |\n| Stat Number | 2rem (32px) | 300 | -0.02em | Dashboard KPI numbers |\n\n**Font Family:** Inter, -apple-system, sans-serif\n\n### Spacing\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Base Unit | 4px grid |\n| Page Padding | 64px horizontal (desktop) |\n| Section Gap | 80px vertical |\n| Card Padding | 24px |\n| Card Gap | 16px |\n| Input Height | 44px |\n| Button Height | 44px |\n\n### Border & Shadows\n\n- **Border radius:** 4px (rounded-sm) on cards, 6px on buttons (rounded-md max)\n- **Shadows:** NONE. Zero box-shadow. Separation achieved via hairline borders.\n- **Border style:** 0.5px solid #F3F4F6\n\n### Status Expression\n\nAll statuses are expressed as 6px colored dots with no text label:\n- Active/New → 6px #10B981 dot\n- Pending → 6px #F59E0B dot\n- Error/Closed → 6px #EF4444 dot\n\n### Sidebar Pattern\n\n- Light background (#F8FAFC)\n- Active item: white bg (#FFFFFF) + 2px left border in primary color\n- Icons: 18px, secondary color (#6B7280)\n- Item padding: 10px 16px\n- Font: 14px, 400 weight\n\n### Button Styles\n\n- **Primary:** Solid #4A90D9 bg, white text, 6px radius, 44px height, 400 weight, no shadow\n- **Secondary/Ghost:** Transparent bg, #4A90D9 text, 6px radius, 44px height\n- **Danger:** Outlined #EF4444 border, transparent bg, 6px radius\n\n### Card Component\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ [Photo — 16:9 aspect ratio]         │\n│                                      │\n├──────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ $1,995/mo                           │\n│ 2 bd · 2 ba · 1,200 sqft            │\n│ 123 Main St, Austin, TX             │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n- Width: 100% (grid item, min 300px)\n- Border: 0.5px #F3F4F6\n- Radius: 4px\n- Padding: 0 (photo flush, text 16px)\n- Photo aspect: 16:9\n- Price: 18px, 500 weight\n- Stats: 14px, 400 weight, secondary color\n- Address: 14px, 400 weight, tertiary color\n\n---\n\n## Page Design Briefs (Representative Pages)\n\n### PAGE 01: Landing\n\n**Layout:** Single column, full-width sections\n**Wrappers:** max-w-[1440px] centered\n\n**Section Flow:**\n1. **Nav:** Logo left, nav links center, CTA buttons right. Pure white bg, 0.5px bottom border.\n2. **Hero:** H1 (72px, 300 weight) \"Find your place.\" with supporting subtitle. Large search bar (560px max, 48px height) with location input + \"Search\" button. No background image — pure typography + whitespace.\n3. **Featured Properties:** Grid of 3 property cards with hairline borders. \"Featured listings\" as H3 section title.\n4. **How It Works:** 3 horizontal steps: Search (magnifier icon) → Compare (cards icon) → Inquire (message icon). Each step: icon 32px, title 18px/500, description 14px/400 secondary.\n5. **CTA Banner:** \"List your property\" — light gray bg (#FAFAFA), two-column: text left, button right.\n6. **Footer:** City links grid, company info, copyright. Hairline top border.\n\n### PAGE 02: Dashboard (Admin)\n\n**Layout:** Sidebar (240px) + Main content area\n\n**Sidebar:**\n- Logo at top\n- Nav items: Overview, Properties, Inquiries, Users\n- Active: white bg + 2px left blue border\n- Inactive: transparent, secondary color text\n- Bottom: user avatar + name, logout\n\n**Main Content:**\n1. **Header:** \"Dashboard\" H2 (36px, 300 weight), date subtitle\n2. **Stats Row:** 4 stat cards in a row — each with 6px colored dot, stat number (32px, 300 weight), label\n3. **Recent Inquiries Table:** Hairline-bordered table with status dots. Columns: Property, Name, Date, Status (dot)\n4. **Recent Properties Table:** Similar table format. Actions: Edit, Archive (text links)\n5. **Quick Actions:** Row of ghost buttons: \"Add Property\", \"View All Inquiries\"\n\n### PAGE 03: Property Detail\n\n**Layout:** Two-column: 65% main / 35% sidebar\n\n**Left Column:**\n1. **Photo Gallery:** 16:9 full-width placeholder with navigation arrows\n2. **Breadcrumb:** \"← Back to search results\" (14px)\n3. **Title + Stats:** H2 \"Modern Downtown Apartment\", price $1,995/mo, 2 bd · 2 ba · 1,200 sqft address\n4. **Actions:** \"Save to Favorites\" ghost button, \"Share\" ghost button\n5. **Description:** Body text, 400 weight\n6. **Amenities Grid:** 2-column list with checkmark icons, 14px text\n7. **Property Details Table:** Hairline-bordered table (Year Built, Parking, Pet Policy, Laundry, A/C)\n8. **Location Map:** Placeholder rectangle (16:9, \"Google Maps\" label)\n9. **Floor Plan:** Placeholder rectangle\n\n**Right Column (Sticky):**\n- **Inquiry Card:** Form — Name, Email, Phone, Message fields, \"Send Message\" primary button. Card with hairline border.\n- **Agent/Property Manager:** Name, contact info\n\n---\n\n## Critical Design Rules\n\n1. **No shadows anywhere.** Separation through whitespace and hairline borders.\n2. **Sparse primary color.** #4A90D9 appears only on CTAs and active states. 95% of UI is grayscale.\n3. **Typography is hierarchy.** Light weights (300-400) for headings, generous sizing. No bold headings.\n4. **One action per card.** Each card has at most one primary CTA.\n5. **6px dots for status.** Never use colored text labels or badges for states.\n6. **Hairline borders (0.5px).** Cards, tables, inputs all use #F3F4F6 0.5px borders.\n7. **No background images.** Photography only in property cards and galleries.\n8. **4px grid.** All spacing follows a strict 4px base unit.\n9. **440px max text width.** Readable line lengths for descriptions.\n10. **Empty states.** Every list/table has a designed empty state with CTA.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_A.md","time":{"start":1779175077750,"end":1779175078051}},"id":"prt_e3f17ed5b001YRNVVCwmCZT3dF","sessionID":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","messageID":"msg_e3f17d790001wPZStGNSGlHjrr"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779175178417,"sessionID":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_01_KtlkjxAQNARhESkxyh9N8942","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md","content":"# DESIGN_SYSTEM_B — Soft Warm\n\n**Archetype:** Soft Warm / Friendly\n**Reference Company:** Notion\n**Variant Code:** B\n\n---\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\n**Core Inspiration:**\n- **Notion** — soft shadows, warm tones, friendly corners, colorful accents\n- **Duolingo** — playful color accents, rounded everything, bouncy interactions\n- **Headspace** — calming warm background, soft illustrations, friendly typography\n- **Airbnb (host side)** — welcoming, rounded cards, warm imagery\n\n**The Three Pillars:**\n- Search & Browsing = Airbnb (rounded cards, warm photo treatment, soft shadows)\n- Admin Dashboard = Notion (soft sidebar, colorful icon accents, gentle borders)\n- Property Detail = Zillow (structured content, warm card treatment)\n\n---\n\n## Design System Quick Reference\n\n### Colors\n\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|-------|-------|-------|\n| Primary | #4A90D9 | Buttons, links, active states |\n| Primary Dark | #3A7BC8 | Button hover |\n| Primary Light | #DBEAFE | Light backgrounds, selected states |\n| Accent Coral | #FF6B6B | Favorites heart, urgent badges |\n| Accent Teal | #0EA5A0 | Success states, property type tags |\n| Accent Amber | #F59E0B | Warning, pending badges |\n| Accent Lavender | #8B5CF6 | Premium/featured badges |\n| Background | #FFFBF5 | Warm cream page background |\n| Surface | #FFFFFF | Card backgrounds, solid white |\n| Surface Warm | #FEF9F0 | Slightly warmer surface |\n| Text Primary | #1E293B | Headings, body text |\n| Text Secondary | #64748B | Labels, metadata |\n| Text Tertiary | #94A3B8 | Placeholders, disabled |\n| Border | #F0E7DB | Warm tone borders |\n| Border Strong | #E8DDD0 | Stronger separators |\n| Sidebar BG | #1A1625 | Warm dark purple |\n| Sidebar Active | #2D2640 | Active item highlight |\n| Sidebar Text | #C4B5FD | Sidebar text color |\n| Sidebar Text Active | #FFFFFF | Active sidebar text |\n| Sunny Yellow | #FCD34D | Feature highlights, badges |\n\n### Typography\n\n| Level | Size | Weight | Letter Spacing | Usage |\n|-------|------|--------|----------------|-------|\n| H1 | 3.5rem (56px) | 600 | -0.03em | Hero sections |\n| H2 | 2rem (32px) | 600 | -0.02em | Page titles |\n| H3 | 1.375rem (22px) | 600 | -0.01em | Section headings |\n| H4 | 1.125rem (18px) | 600 | normal | Card titles |\n| Body | 1rem (16px) | 400 | normal | Main content |\n| Small | 0.875rem (14px) | 500 | normal | Metadata |\n| Caption | 0.75rem (12px) | 500 | normal | Fine print |\n| Stat Number | 2.25rem (36px) | 700 | -0.02em | Dashboard KPI numbers |\n\n**Font Family:** Inter, -apple-system, sans-serif\n**Default Weight:** 500-600 for headings, 400-500 for body\n\n### Spacing\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Base Unit | 8px grid |\n| Page Padding | 48px horizontal (desktop) |\n| Section Gap | 64px vertical |\n| Card Padding | 24px |\n| Card Gap | 24px |\n| Input Height | 48px |\n| Button Height | 48px |\n\n### Border & Shadows\n\n- **Border radius:** 16px on cards (rounded-2xl), 24px on buttons (rounded-full for pill buttons)\n- **Shadows:** Soft warm drop shadows on cards — 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04), 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.02)\n- **Hover shadow:** 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06) — gentle lift\n- **Border style:** 1px solid #F0E7DB\n\n### Status Expression\n\nPastel-colored pill badges with matching text:\n- New → #DBEAFE bg, #1E40AF text (blue pill)\n- Read → #E0E7FF bg, #4338CA text (indigo pill)\n- Responded → #D1FAE5 bg, #065F46 text (green pill)\n- Archived → #F3F4F6 bg, #6B7280 text (gray pill)\n- Pending → #FEF3C7 bg, #92400E text (amber pill)\n\n### Sidebar Pattern\n\n- Dark warm background (#1A1625)\n- Active item: #2D2640 bg, white text, colored icon\n- Inactive items: transparent bg, #C4B5FD text\n- Icons: 20px, colored per section (blue=properties, coral=inquiries, teal=users)\n- Item padding: 12px 20px\n- Font: 14px, 500 weight\n- Pill-shaped corners: rounded-full\n\n### Button Styles\n\n- **Primary:** Solid #4A90D9 bg, white text, rounded-full (24px radius), 48px height, 600 weight, soft shadow\n- **Secondary:** White bg, #4A90D9 border (1px), rounded-full\n- **Ghost:** Transparent, #4A90D9 text, rounded-full\n- **Danger:** #FEE2E2 bg, #DC2626 text, rounded-full\n- **Hover:** Lift effect (translateY(-1px) + shadow increase)\n\n### Card Component\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ ┌────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│ │ [Photo — 16:9, rounded 12px]  │   │\n│ └────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│ $1,995/mo              [♡ Save]     │\n│ 2 bd · 2 ba · 1,200 sqft            │\n│ 123 Main St, Austin, TX             │\n│ [New] [Pet Friendly]                │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n- Width: 100% (grid item, min 320px)\n- Border: 1px #F0E7DB\n- Radius: 16px (rounded-2xl)\n- Padding: 20px\n- Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)\n- Hover shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\n- Photo radius: 12px inside card\n- Price: 22px, 700 weight, primary-dark\n- Stats: 14px, 500 weight, secondary color\n- Badges: 12px, 600 weight, rounded-full pills in accent colors\n\n---\n\n## Page Design Briefs (Representative Pages)\n\n### PAGE 01: Landing\n\n**Layout:** Single column, full-width sections on warm cream background\n**Wrappers:** max-w-[1440px] centered\n\n**Section Flow:**\n1. **Nav:** Warm cream bg, pill-shaped login/signup buttons. Logo left (bold, primary color).\n2. **Hero:** H1 (56px, 600 weight) \"Find your nest.\" with subtle emoji accent. Subtitle in secondary color. Large rounded-full search bar with decorative icon prefix, pill-shaped \"Search\" button. Soft gradient background: radial gradient from white to warm cream.\n3. **Popular Cities:** Row of 6 rounded-2xl city cards with soft shadows, gradient image overlays, city name + property count.\n4. **Featured Properties:** Grid of 3-4 pill-shaped property cards. \"✨ Featured listings\" section title with accent color.\n5. **How It Works:** 3-step cards with soft warm bg (#FEF9F0), large emoji icons, rounded-2xl containers.\n6. **CTA Banner:** Warm gradient bg (cream → coral-tinted), rounded-3xl container, friendly CTA text.\n7. **Footer:** Cream background, rounded section dividers, city links in pill badges.\n\n### PAGE 02: Dashboard (Admin)\n\n**Layout:** Sidebar (250px, warm dark purple) + Main content area (warm cream bg)\n\n**Sidebar:**\n- Dark purple (#1A1625) background\n- Logo: white text, lavender accent dot\n- Nav items with colored SVG-style icons: Properties (blue), Inquiries (coral), Users (teal)\n- Active: #2D2640 bg, white text, pill shape (rounded-full)\n- User section: avatar circle, name in white, role in lavender\n\n**Main Content:**\n1. **Header:** \"Welcome back, Admin 👋\" H2 (32px, 600 weight), date in secondary color\n2. **Stats Row:** 4 pill-shaped stat cards with warm shadow, colored icon circles (36px), large stat numbers (36px, 700 weight), colorful accent borders\n3. **Recent Inquiries:** Rounded-2xl card table. Pastel pill badges for statuses.\n4. **Recent Properties:** Same card style. Rounded-full \"Edit\" and \"Archive\" pill buttons.\n5. **Quick Actions:** Row of colorful pill buttons with icon prefixes, soft shadows.\n\n### PAGE 03: Property Detail\n\n**Layout:** Two-column: 65% main / 35% sidebar\n\n**Left Column:**\n1. **Photo Gallery:** Rounded-2xl container with large placeholder photos, pill-shaped navigation dots\n2. **Breadcrumb:** \"← Back to search\" pill link with arrow\n3. **Title + Stats:** H2 (32px, 600 weight), price in large bold with primary color\n4. **Quick Stats:** Row of pill badges: \"2 Beds\", \"2 Baths\", \"1,200 sqft\"\n5. **Save + Share:** Pill buttons — \"♡ Save\" (coral accent when active), \"Share\" (gray)\n6. **Description:** Warm card container, body text, 400 weight\n7. **Amenities:** Grid of pastel-colored pill badges with check icon prefixes\n8. **Property Details:** Rounded-2xl card with key-value pairs\n9. **Location Map:** Rounded-2xl placeholder with warm border\n10. **Similar Properties:** Row of 3 rounded-2xl property cards\n\n**Right Column (Sticky):**\n- **Inquiry Card:** Rounded-2xl white card with soft shadow. Form fields with rounded-full inputs. Pill-shaped \"Send Message\" primary button.\n- **Property Manager Card:** Rounded-2xl card with avatar circle, name, contact info.\n\n---\n\n## Critical Design Rules\n\n1. **Soft warm shadows everywhere.** 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04) on all cards. Gentle lift on hover.\n2. **Rounded everything.** Cards 16px (rounded-2xl), buttons 24px (rounded-full), inputs 24px (rounded-full).\n3. **Colorful accents.** 4 accent colors used throughout: coral, teal, amber, lavender.\n4. **Warm cream background (NEVER pure white).** #FFFBF5 page background, distinct from white cards.\n5. **Pastel pill badges.** Statuses use colored background pills, never dots.\n6. **Dark warm sidebar.** Distinct from page background, cozy feel.\n7. **Pill-shaped buttons only.** No rectangular buttons anywhere.\n8. **8px grid system.** Spacing aligns to 8px increments.\n9. **Emoji accents in empty states and headers.** Friendly, human touch.\n10. **Lift hover effects.** translateY(-1px) on all interactive cards/buttons.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_B.md","time":{"start":1779175178139,"end":1779175178415}},"id":"prt_e3f19392a001ZkEQXpdWg0RpoZ","sessionID":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","messageID":"msg_e3f17d790001wPZStGNSGlHjrr"}}
