| #FBBF24 | Warning status |\n| Neon Red | #F87171 | Error status |\n| Neon Blue | #60A5FA | Info status, links |\n| Neon Purple | #A78BFA | Premium/featured |\n| Sidebar BG | #070B14 | Darker than page background |\n| Sidebar Active | rgba(74,144,217,0.15) | Active item with primary tint |\n| Sidebar Border | rgba(74,144,217,0.3) | 2px left accent on active |\n\n### Typography\n\n| Level | Size | Weight | Letter Spacing | Usage |\n|-------|------|--------|----------------|-------|\n| H1 | 4rem (64px) | 700 | -0.04em | Hero sections |\n| H2 | 2.25rem (36px) | 700 | -0.03em | Page titles |\n| H3 | 1.5rem (24px) | 600 | -0.02em | Section headings |\n| H4 | 1.125rem (18px) | 600 | -0.01em | Card titles |\n| Body | 1rem (16px) | 500 | normal | Main content (increased weight for dark readability) |\n| Small | 0.875rem (14px) | 500 | normal | Metadata |\n| Caption | 0.75rem (12px) | 500 | normal | Fine print |\n| Stat Number | 2.5rem (40px) | 800 | -0.03em | Dashboard KPI numbers |\n\n**Font Family:** Inter, -apple-system, sans-serif\n**Additional:** Tight letter-spacing for headings (-0.03 to -0.04em)\n\n### Spacing\n\n| Token | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| Base Unit | 4px grid |\n| Page Padding | 80px horizontal (desktop) |\n| Section Gap | 80px vertical |\n| Card Padding | 28px |\n| Card Gap | 20px |\n| Input Height | 48px |\n| Button Height | 48px |\n\n### Border & Shadows\n\n- **Border radius:** 12px on cards (rounded-xl), 12px on buttons\n- **Glass cards:** rgba(255,255,255,0.05) bg + backdrop-filter: blur(12px) + border rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n- **Shadows:** Glow shadows only — 0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15) on primary elements\n- **Card shadow:** 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3) — depth through darkness\n- **Hover:** Glow intensifies + subtle scale (1.02)\n- **Border style:** 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n\n### Status Expression\n\nNeon-colored dots with glow effect:\n- Active/New → #4ADE80 dot + 0 0 8px rgba(74,222,128,0.5) glow\n- Pending → #FBBF24 dot + 0 0 8px rgba(251,191,36,0.5) glow\n- Error/Closed → #F87171 dot + 0 0 8px rgba(248,113,113,0.5) glow\n- Displays as 8px dot with text label next to it, 12px, 600 weight\n\n### Sidebar Pattern\n\n- Darker background (#070B14) — distinct from page background\n- Active item: rgba(74,144,217,0.15) bg + 2px left primary gradient border\n- Inactive items: transparent, text-secondary (#94A3B8)\n- Section dividers: rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\n- Icons: 20px, text-secondary, glow on active\n- Item padding: 12px 24px\n- Font: 14px, 500 weight\n- Bottom user section: separated by gradient divider line\n\n### Button Styles\n\n- **Primary:** Gradient bg (primary → purple), white text, 12px radius, 48px height, 600 weight, glow shadow\n- **Hover:** Glow intensifies, gradient shifts slightly, scale(1.02)\n- **Secondary:** Transparent bg, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) border, white text\n- **Ghost:** Transparent, text-primary, glow on hover\n- **Danger:** rgba(248,113,113,0.15) bg, #F87171 text, neon red border\n\n### Card Component\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ ┌────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│ │ [Photo — 16:9, rounded 8px]   │   │\n│ │   gradient overlay at bottom  │   │\n│ └────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│ $1,995/mo              [♡]          │\n│ 2 bd · 2 ba · 1,200 sqft            │\n│ 123 Main St, Austin, TX             │\n│ [NEW] [Pet Friendly]                │\n└──────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n- Width: 100% (grid item, min 320px)\n- Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) + backdrop-blur(12px)\n- Border: 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\n- Radius: 12px (rounded-xl)\n- Padding: 0 (photo section flush), 20px text area\n- Shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\n- Hover: glow border + scale(1.02)\n- Photo: rounded 8px inside card, gradient overlay\n- Price: 20px, 700 weight, #F1F5F9 with subtle text-glow\n- Stats: 14px, 500 weight, text-secondary\n- Badges: 10px, 600 weight, neon-colored, glass bg\n\n---\n\n## Page Design Briefs (Representative Pages)\n\n### PAGE 01: Landing\n\n**Layout:** Single column, full-width sections on deep navy background\n**Wrappers:** max-w-[1440px] centered\n\n**Section Flow:**\n1. **Nav:** Glass nav bar (backdrop-blur, rgba(7,11,20,0.8)), logo with gradient text, nav links, gradient CTA buttons.\n2. **Hero:** Dramatic H1 (64px, 700 weight) with gradient text effect. Subtle animated background: mesh gradient or radial glow. Large glass-morphism search bar with icon, gradient \"Search\" button.\n3. **Stats Strip:** \"10,000+ listings · 50+ cities · 5,000+ happy renters\" in neon-colored numbers with glow.\n4. **Featured Properties:** Grid of 3-4 glass-morphism property cards with gradient photo overlays. \"🔥 Trending now\" section title with warm neon glow.\n5. **How It Works:** 3-step horizontal layout. Each step: gradient icon circle with glow, title, description. Connected by subtle gradient lines.\n6. **CTA Banner:** Dark gradient container with glass card inside, neon CTA button with glow animation.\n7. **Footer:** Deep background, subtle top border glow, link columns in secondary text.\n\n### PAGE 02: Dashboard (Admin)\n\n**Layout:** Sidebar (260px, darker #070B14) + Main content area\n\n**Sidebar:**\n- Darker background (#070B14) distinct from page\n- Logo: gradient text effect (primary → purple)\n- Nav items with neon-colored icons: Properties (blue glow), Inquiries (green glow), Users (purple glow)\n- Active: rgba(74,144,217,0.15) bg + 2px left gradient border\n- Gradient divider lines between sections\n- User: avatar with glow ring, name, role\n\n**Main Content:**\n1. **Header:** \"Dashboard\" H2 (36px, 700 weight), breadcrumb trail, date with subtle glow\n2. **Stats Row:** 4 glass stat cards in a row — gradient icon circles (40px), neon stat numbers (40px, 800 weight), labels. Each card with subtle colored glow border on hover.\n3. **Charts Area:** Placeholder area with glass container, \"Revenue / Inquiries\" labels\n4. **Recent Inquiries Table:** Glass container table with neon status dots. Alternating row backgrounds (rgba(255,255,255,0.02)).\n5. **Recent Properties:** Same glass table. Gradient \"Edit\" and ghost \"Archive\" buttons.\n6. **Quick Actions:** Row of gradient outline buttons with icon prefixes.\n\n### PAGE 03: Property Detail\n\n**Layout:** Two-column: 65% main / 35% sidebar\n\n**Left Column:**\n1. **Photo Gallery:** Large glass container (16:9), gradient photo placeholders, glowing navigation arrows, neon dot indicators\n2. **Breadcrumb:** \"← Back to search\" ghost link with glow on hover\n3. **Title + Stats:** H2 (36px, 700 weight), price in large gradient text with glow. Quick stats in glass pill badges.\n4. **Save + Share:** Gradient-outline \"♡ Save\" button, ghost \"Share\" button\n5. **Description:** Glass card with text content\n6. **Amenities:** Grid of glass pill badges with neon icon prefixes\n7. **Property Details Table:** Glass container with glowing accent borders on key rows\n8. **Location Map:** Dark-themed placeholder with neon marker dot\n9. **Similar Properties:** Horizontal scroll of 3 glass property cards\n\n**Right Column (Sticky):**\n- **Inquiry Card:** Glass container with gradient top border accent. Form inputs with glass bg and subtle borders. Gradient \"Send Message\" button with glow effect.\n- **Property Manager Card:** Glass container with avatar circle (glow ring), name, contact info, neon \"Call\" and \"Email\" buttons.\n\n---\n\n## Critical Design Rules\n\n1. **Deep navy background (#0B0F1A).** Never lighter than this. Cards are glass (translucent), not solid.\n2. **Glassmorphism everywhere.** rgba(255,255,255,0.05) bg + backdrop-blur(12px) on all cards.\n3. **Gradient primary.** #4A90D9 is never used solid — always as part of a gradient with purple or blue.\n4. **Glow shadows.** 0 0 20px rgba(74,144,217,0.15) on primary elements. No flat shadows.\n5. **Neon status indicators.** 8px dots with colored glow effects. Always with text labels.\n6. **Dark sidebar distinct from page.** #070B14 sidebar vs #0B0F1A page background.\n7. **Typographic emphasis through weight and tracking.** 700-800 weight for headings, tight letter-spacing.\n8. **Subtle scale on hover.** scale(1.02) + glow increase for interactive cards.\n9. **4px grid system.** Strict spacing base.\n10. **High contrast text for readability.** Minimum 500 weight for body text on dark backgrounds.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_C.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/design/DESIGN_SYSTEM_C.md","time":{"start":1779175288034,"end":1779175288357}},"id":"prt_e3f1ac156001WpqUnmt3ii5U1C","sessionID":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","messageID":"msg_e3f17d790001wPZStGNSGlHjrr"}}
