{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779175900484,"sessionID":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_00_Ea2EPYrvq5fQ0XmHYu6b4226","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Generate Variant A HTML files","subagent_type":"general","prompt":"You are generating 3 self-contained HTML files for a rental property platform called \"NestFind\". These files are DESIGN VARIATION A — \"Editorial Minimal\" (inspired by Linear.app).\n\nCRITICAL RULES FOR EVERY FILE:\n1. Root wrapper must have `class=\"max-w-[1440px]\"` or inline `max-width: 1440px` AND `class=\"mx-auto\"` centered.\n2. Every file MUST include this exact nav element (adjust the page name and active state):\n```html\n<nav class=\"var-nav-bar fixed top-4 right-4 flex gap-2 bg-black/80 px-3 py-2 rounded z-50 text-xs\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n  <a href=\"A-01-landing.html\" style=\"color:white;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;\">A</a>\n  <a href=\"B-01-landing.html\" style=\"color:#9CA3AF;text-decoration:none;\">B</a>\n  <a href=\"C-01-landing.html\" style=\"color:#9CA3AF;text-decoration:none;\">C</a>\n</nav>\n```\nFor dashboard pages, replace -01- with -02- and for detail pages use -03-. Active link is bold white, others gray.\n\n3. All CSS must be inline or in a &lt;style&gt; block within the HTML. No external dependencies.\n4. Use realistic placeholder text (not \"lorem ipsum\"). Actual property names, prices, addresses.\n5. Photo areas should use CSS gradients as placeholders (e.g., linear-gradient for image areas).\n\nDESIGN SYSTEM A — Editorial Minimal:\n- Background: #FFFFFF (pure white)\n- Primary: #4A90D9 (used SPARINGLY — only CTAs and active states)\n- Text: #1A1A1A primary, #6B7280 secondary, #9CA3AF tertiary\n- Borders: 0.5px solid #F3F4F6 — HAIRLINE, barely visible\n- NO SHADOWS anywhere. Zero box-shadow.\n- Border radius: 4px on cards max, 6px on buttons\n- Typography: Inter font, 300 weight for H1/H2 headings, 400 for body. No bold headings.\n- Status: 6px colored dots only (no text labels)\n- Cards: white bg, hairline border, no shadow\n- Sidebar: #F8FAFC background, active item gets white bg + 2px left blue border\n- Buttons: solid #4A90D9, 6px radius, 44px height, no shadow\n- Property cards: 16:9 photo ratio, price 18px/500, stats 14px/400, hairline border\n\n=== FILE 1: A-01-landing.html ===\nFull landing page. Sections in order:\n1. NAV: Logo \"nestfind\" (left, 18px, 500 weight), nav links (Search, Favorites center), Sign In / Sign Up buttons (right, Sign Up is solid blue)\n2. HERO: H1 \"Find your place.\" (72px, 300 weight, #1A1A1A), subtitle \"Discover rental properties that feel like home.\" (18px, #6B7280), large search input (560px max-width, 48px height, hairline border, placeholder \"Search by city, neighborhood, or ZIP...\") + \"Search\" button (solid blue, 44px)\n3. FEATURED PROPERTIES: \"Featured listings\" section heading (24px, 400 weight). Grid of 3 property cards side by side. Each card: gradient photo placeholder (16:9), price big \"$2,450/mo\" / \"$1,895/mo\" / \"$3,200/mo\", stats \"2 bd · 2 ba · 1,150 sqft\", address \"123 Main St, Austin, TX\". Hairline border, 4px radius, NO shadow.\n4. HOW IT WORKS: 3 horizontal steps with icons (use text/unicode placeholders): \"01 Search\" → \"02 Compare\" → \"03 Inquire\". Each step: small number, title, description. Light and minimal.\n5. CTA BANNER: Light gray (#FAFAFA) full-width strip, \"List your property on NestFind\" heading, paragraph, \"Get Started\" outline button.\n6. FOOTER: 4-column link grid (Popular Cities, For Renters, For Landlords, About), copyright line, hairline top border.\n\n=== FILE 2: A-02-dashboard.html ===\nAdmin dashboard. Layout: sidebar (240px) + main content.\n1. SIDEBAR (#F8FAFC bg, 240px): \n   - Logo \"nestfind\" at top\n   - Nav: Overview (active — white bg, 2px left blue border), Properties, Inquiries, Users (inactive — transparent, #6B7280 text)\n   - Bottom: user avatar circle placeholder, \"Admin User\", \"admin@nestfind.com\", \"Logout\" link\n2. MAIN HEADER: \"Dashboard\" (36px, 300 weight), \"Welcome back\" subtitle\n3. STATS ROW: 4 stat cards in a row. Each: 6px colored dot + big number (32px, 300 weight) + label. \"124 Total Properties\" (blue dot), \"48 New Inquiries\" (green dot), \"3,240 Active Users\" (green dot), \"12 Pending\" (amber dot). Cards: white, hairline border, NO shadow.\n4. RECENT INQUIRIES: Table with hairline borders. Columns: Property, Name, Date, Status (6px dot). 4-5 rows of data.\n5. RECENT PROPERTIES: Table with hairline borders. Columns: Title, Price, Status (6px dot), Actions (Edit/Archive text links). 4-5 rows.\n6. QUICK ACTIONS: Row of ghost buttons: \"Add Property\", \"View All Inquiries\", \"Manage Users\"\n\n=== FILE 3: A-03-detail.html ===\nProperty detail page. Two-column: 65% left / 35% right.\n1. PHOTO GALLERY: Large gradient placeholder (16:9, full-width), left/right arrow indicators\n2. BREADCRUMB: \"← Back to search results\" link (14px, #9CA3AF)\n3. TITLE + STATS: H2 \"Modern Downtown Apartment\" (36px, 300 weight), price \"$1,995/mo\" (24px, 500 weight, #1A1A1A), \"2 bd · 2 ba · 1,150 sqft · Apartment\", \"123 Main St, Austin, TX 78701\" (#6B7280)\n4. ACTIONS: \"Save to Favorites\" ghost button, \"Share\" ghost button\n5. DESCRIPTION: \"Overview\" section (18px, 500 weight heading), 3-4 sentences of realistic description (400 weight, #1A1A1A)\n6. AMENITIES: 2-column grid with ✓ checkmarks. \"✓ In-unit laundry\", \"✓ Parking included\", \"✓ Pet friendly\", \"✓ Central A/C\", \"✓ Fitness center\", \"✓ Swimming pool\"\n7. PROPERTY DETAILS TABLE: Hairline bordered table. Year Built: 2019, Property Type: Apartment, Parking: 1 reserved spot, Pet Policy: Cats & dogs allowed, Laundry: In-unit, A/C: Central\n8. LOCATION MAP: Gradient placeholder rectangle (400x250px) with \"📍 Map View\" text\n9. FLOOR PLAN: Gradient placeholder rectangle\n10. SIMILAR PROPERTIES: \"Similar properties nearby\" heading, row of 3 small property cards\n11. RIGHT COLUMN (sticky): Inquiry card with hairline border. \"Interested in this property?\" heading. Form: Name, Email, Phone, Message (textarea) inputs (all 44px height, hairline border). \"Send Message\" solid blue button. Below: Property manager card with name \"Sarah Johnson\", \"Property Manager\", email.\n\nWrite these 3 files to:\n- /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/A-01-landing.html\n- /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/A-02-dashboard.html\n- /Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/A-03-detail.html\n\nMake each file substantial and visually convincing (not barebones). Use rich content, realistic data. Each file should be a complete, self-contained HTML document with embedded CSS styles that faithfully represents the Editorial Minimal design system.\n"},"output":"task_id: ses_1c0e23ec5ffevRPeRh9RNMWlbh (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nAll 3 files created at `/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/design/variations/`:\n\n| File | Size | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| `A-01-landing.html` | 12KB | Landing — hero search, 3 featured cards, how-it-works, CTA, footer |\n| `A-02-dashboard.html` | 13KB | Admin — sidebar, 4 stat cards, inquiries table, properties table, quick actions |\n| `A-03-detail.html` | 17KB | Detail — 2-col layout, gallery, amenities, details table, map, floor plan, inquiry form, manager card |\n\nDesign system faithfully applied: no shadows, hairline 0.5px #F3F4F6 borders, 4px card radius / 6px button radius, #4A90D9 only on CTAs/active states, 300-weight headings, Inter font, 6px status dots, #F8FAFC sidebar with 2px blue active indicator, gradient photo placeholders, realistic data throughout.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"parentSessionId":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","sessionId":"ses_1c0e23ec5ffevRPeRh9RNMWlbh","model":{"modelID":"deepseek-v4-pro","providerID":"opencode-go"},"truncated":false},"title":"Generate Variant A HTML files","time":{"start":1779175375168,"end":1779175900483}},"id":"prt_e3f1cac2a001L9ZKxJ2n7TTyBP","sessionID":"ses_1c0e9e840ffe9Rmyds03EgTY5k","messageID":"msg_e3f1c6f1c001x4MV3MDQC9oLEm"}}
